overview: The user initiated a project to enhance a sleep questionnaire
  application by adding database capabilities and an admin dashboard for client
  data access. The existing application already handled the interactive
  questionnaire and PDF report generation. The implementation focused on
  integrating a PostgreSQL database (NeonDB) using Prisma to store detailed
  questionnaire responses, including de-identified demographic data. A
  straightforward password-based authentication system was developed to secure
  access to a new admin dashboard. This dashboard provides a user-friendly
  interface for viewing submitted responses, complete with pagination and a CSV
  export feature. The questionnaire form was modified to automatically save
  submitted data to the new database, ensuring all SOW requirements for data
  capture and access were met with a simple, efficient approach.
